name: ext_R5_HealthcareService_contact
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.HealthcareService.contact for use in FHIR R3
description: This cross-version extension represents HealthcareService.contact from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/HealthcareService|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R3.

element.short: Official contact details for the HealthcareService
element.definition: The contact details of communication devices available relevant to the specific HealthcareService. This can include addresses, phone numbers, fax numbers, mobile numbers, email addresses and web sites.
